            <li>(c) To comply with applicable laws and regulatory requirements.</li>
        </ul>
    
        <p>2.2. We may collect your Personal Data in various ways, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>(a) When you submit forms, applications, or feedback to us;</li>
            <li>(b) When you provide information as part of our services;</li>
            <li>(c) When you interact with our customer service team through various channels;</li>
            <li>(d) When you use our websites, mobile applications, or other digital services;</li>
            <li>(e) When you respond to our requests for additional information;</li>
